parse.title: List of presidential trips made by Moncef Marzouki

text.*:
The President Moncef Marzouki.

This is a list of presidential trips made by Moncef Marzouki, the 3rd President of Tunisia. As of December 2014[update], Marzouki has made 38 international trips to 25 different countries since his presidency began with his 13 December 2011 inauguration until the transfer of power on 31 December 2014, in addition to many more trips made domestically within the Tunisia which are not shown on this list.

  • 2 2012
  • 3 2013
  • 4 2014
  • 5 References
